                "<strong style='color:#16A34A'>вң… REGLA DE DECISIГ“N (Score + WR + C-Score):</strong><br>"
                "рҹ”ҙ <strong>WR histГіrico &lt;50%</strong> вҶ’ рҹҡ« NO ENTRAR siempre В· WR mide cuГЎntas seГұales similares ganaron<br>"
                "рҹ”Ҙ <strong>ScoreвүҘ15 + C-ScoreвүҘ80</strong> вҶ’ ENTRAR PLENO В· catalizador excepcional<br>"
                "рҹҹў <strong>ScoreвүҘ15 + C-ScoreвүҘ65</strong> вҶ’ вң… ENTRAR В· catalizador sГіlido<br>"
